Costs for the Finnish municipal sector
====================================

In the municipal sector total costs average 10,78% of the organisations’ payroll. 

In the whole sector, costs based on 2014 payroll figures total `r round(0.1078*(16.67+1.360))`billion euros

If all the organisations were on the level of the most cost-effective organisation there would be an annual saving of `r round(0.0296*(16.67+1.360) * 1000)` million euros. The actual savings potential is bigger because even the most effective organisation has margin for intensification in their disability management.  

