Disability management scoring system
====================================

Keva’s cross professional team has rated organisations’ disability management with a scoring matrix. Each element scores 0-10 points (max 60 points)

<small>
Elements are:

* structure of procedures to support capacity to work 
* extent and homogeneity of procedures to support capacity to work 
* training in procedures to support capacity to work 
* creating procedures to support capacity to work 
* sick leave reporting
* strategic disability management
</small>

